<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1852] OffsetCommitRequest can commit offset on unknown topic</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1852</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, we allow an offset to be committed to Kafka, even when the topic/partition for the offset doesn&apos;t exist. We probably should disallow that and send an error back in that case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
